<plot>Fight for the focuses on the physical, social and economic impacts of global warming, and stresses the need for a change in politics - but also in behavior. It sheds light on the ideas and opinions of our younger generation, and their struggle to be heard. It investigates both the science behind climate change, and technologies that will bring us into the new 'green' future. Many are interviewed and these include various experts and green tech companies.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?193800</url></doc>
